lalt + ctrl + shift - f : aerospace fullscreen
lalt + ctrl - f: aerospace layout floating tiling

lalt + shift - left : aerospace join-with left
lalt + shift - down : aerospace join-with down
lalt + shift - up : aerospace join-with up 
lalt + shift - right : aerospace join-with right

# See: https://nikitabobko.github.io/AeroSpace/commands#focus
lalt - h : aerospace focus left
lalt - j : aerospace focus down
lalt - k : aerospace focus up
lalt - l : aerospace focus right

# See: https://nikitabobko.github.io/AeroSpace/commands#resize
lalt + shift - 0x2C : aerospace resize smart -50
lalt + shift - 0x1E : aerospace resize smart +50

# See: https://nikitabobko.github.io/AeroSpace/commands#layout
lalt - 0x2B : aerospace layout accordion horizontal vertical
lalt - 0x2F : aerospace layout tiles horizontal vertical

# See: https://nikitabobko.github.io/AeroSpace/commands#move
lalt + shift - h : aerospace move left
lalt + shift - j : aerospace move down 
lalt + shift - k : aerospace move up 
lalt + shift - l : aerospace move right 

# See: https://nikitabobko.github.io/AeroSpace/commands#workspace
lalt - 1 : aerospace workspace 1
lalt - 2 : aerospace workspace 2
lalt - 3 : aerospace workspace 3
lalt - 4 : aerospace workspace 4

# See: https://nikitabobko.github.io/AeroSpace/commands#move-node-to-workspace
lalt + shift - 1 : aerospace move-node-to-workspace 1 --focus-follows-window
lalt + shift - 2 : aerospace move-node-to-workspace 2 --focus-follows-window
lalt + shift - 3 : aerospace move-node-to-workspace 3 --focus-follows-window
lalt + shift - 4 : aerospace move-node-to-workspace 4 --focus-follows-window

lalt - tab : aerospace focus-back-and-forth
lalt + shift - tab : aerospace workspace-back-and-forth

# See: https://nikitabobko.github.io/AeroSpace/commands#mode
lalt + shift - return : aerospace mode apps 
